  Inline 'GTK_MAJ_VER' variable value.

*glade-0.12.5.0-r2 (14 Dec 2014)

  14 Dec 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +glade-0.12.5.0-r2.ebuild,
  -glade-0.12.0.ebuild:
  Loosen glib and gtk deps in glade-0.12.5.0-r2

  25 Jul 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> glade-0.12.0.ebuild,
  glade-0.12.1-r1.ebuild, glade-0.12.1.ebuild, glade-0.12.5.0-r1.ebuild:
  Drop trailing '.' from description.

  25 Jul 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop redundant '<maintainer>' field, leave only '<herd>'.

  05 Jun 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> glade-0.12.1-r1.ebuild:
  Use unmodified 'gtk2hsTypeGen' (bug #512474 by Pawe≈Ç Hajdan, Jr.).

*glade-0.12.5.0-r1 (12 Dec 2013)

  12 Dec 2013; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +glade-0.12.5.0-r1.ebuild,
  glade-0.12.0.ebuild, glade-0.12.1-r1.ebuild, glade-0.12.1.ebuild:
  Bump glade to glade-0.12.5.0-r1. Move cairo, glib, gio, gtk2hs-buildtools,
  pango to slot 0.

  07 Dec 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> glade-0.12.1-r1.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug #488808

  24 Nov 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> glade-0.12.1-r1.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug #488808

*glade-0.12.1-r1 (03 Apr 2013)

